00:20:25.010 --> 00:20:30.240
in the field of trying to defend
those who are victims of abuse.

00:20:30.240 --> 00:20:31.520
We'll have a copy here.

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:33.535
And Victor Boutros
who's my co-author,

00:20:33.535 --> 00:20:35.010
I always want to recognize him.

