00:20:44.590 --> 00:20:48.860
So we would love for you to
buy the book and to share that.

00:20:48.860 --> 00:20:50.440
The second thing
we'd like to do is

00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:52.890
actually, have you look
at a piece of video

00:20:52.890 --> 00:20:57.319
