00:20:57.319 --> 00:20:59.110
Because obviously,
we've written this book,

00:20:59.110 --> 00:21:00.870
it's got 40 pages of footnotes.

00:21:00.870 --> 00:21:03.550
It really takes you into sort
of the deep intellectual case

00:21:03.550 --> 00:21:04.666
about what's going on.

00:21:04.666 --> 00:21:06.040
But for most of
us, in many ways,

00:21:06.040 --> 00:21:10.700
it's important just for us
to get a heart level almost

00:21:10.700 --> 00:21:12.930
sense of what this
challenge is looking

00:21:12.930 --> 00:21:15.840
like for the common person,
and also what the promise is.

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:17.740
So if you've got two
minutes, let's have

00:21:17.740 --> 00:21:20.800
a look at this
