00:29:46.010 --> 00:29:48.130
AUDIENCE: So the
first question was

00:29:48.130 --> 00:29:51.440
people are looking at is from
an economic modeling standpoint.

00:29:51.440 --> 00:29:54.060
Are people looking at it
also from a public health

00:29:54.060 --> 00:29:55.780
standpoint?

00:29:55.780 --> 00:29:57.602
